steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
Debug step:
When I navigate to menu "Database" with submenu "Database Editor"
Then I should see Database screen display
When I add new table with Name "jitmodulelinelogin010" and Comment "Testing Module for Line Login"
Then I should see the table with Name "jitmodulelinelogin010" display
When I navigate to menu "Modules" without submenu
Then I should see Modules screen display
When I add module "Line Login"
Then I should see Header "Production" is collapsed
Then I should see Header "Staging" is collapsed
Then I should see Header "Development" is collapsed
When I expand Header "Production"
When I expand Header "Staging"
When I expand Header "Development"
When I press Save button popover popup without wait
Then I should see inline error message of multi dropdown with label "Associated users tables" has message "Associated users tables are required"
Debug step:
Then I should see inline error message of textbox has Header "Production" and label "Client ID" with message "Client ID is required"
Then I should see inline error message of textbox has Header "Production" and label "Secret Key" with message "Secret Key is required"
Then I should see inline error message of textbox has Header "Staging" and label "Client ID" with message "Client ID is required"
Then I should see inline error message of textbox has Header "Staging" and label "Secret Key" with message "Secret Key is required"

Then I should see inline error message of textbox has Header "Development" and label "Secret Key" with message "Secret Key is required"

When I input textbox has Header "Production" and label "Secret Key" with value "jitera Secret Key"

Then I should see eyed textbox with Header "Staging" and label "Secret Key" with value "jitera Secret Key"
